efficiency indoors compared to outdoor wild fruitings, or outdoor fruitings in beds with unpasteurized substrates.&lt;br /&gt;RR</content>\n<name>RogerRabbit</name>\n<next>14795261</next>\n<prev>14795234</prev>\n<first>14791334</first>\n<last>19090415</last>\n<when>1311133341</when>\n<utime>07/20/11 06:42 AM</utime>\n</post>"}